title: Is Justin Bieber's new song Yummy nothing more than Trap Muzak? - Quora

response.answer_text: I think it is. To me it just seems lazy and as if he is jumping on the bandwagon. Others have compared it or at least the video to a Tik Tok video. It’s very repetitive and does not say much. Other gimmicky songs at least progress from the first idea. He is also at odds with the style not growing up in the area or living the lifestyle. This song is relatable and we have all been in this situation. LunchMoney Lewis - Bills (Official Video)
